                    "body": "{quote}\r\nWeston Pace that might be related to the fact that interupting doesn't work here?\r\n{quote}\r\n\r\nYes, that seems very likely.  We don't have cancellation support in Acero today (though it shouldn't be too hard to add).  Just to be clear though, there are still two problems right?\r\n\r\n1. You cannot cancel the write dataset operation\r\n2. The generator should wrap up and finish but the write dataset operation is hanging indefinitely\r\n\r\nAlso, it seems this was filed some time ago.  Very sorry for missing the first ping.",
